      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BELIEVE IN DREAMS (8) resumes from a spell of eight months after closing off last campaign in good form, the last run being a solid third at Wagga. Readied with two trials, winning the latest. Draws for a trail and if he gets the gaps he could kick off this campaign on a winning note. ROCK SPIRIT (9) made a solid return after six months when finishing 3.5 metres from the winner in third at Wagga after being close to the pace throughout. May need luck from the second row but should be improved. IDEAL LILLY (1) will be fitter for recent racing and should get her chance from the ace draw. BETTORBYTHESEA (2) didn't do a bad job when fifth at Wagga last time out and draws to advantage.",
